Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,风好大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全入秋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:25.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了有热饮的季节了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,天地间已完全是一副秋天的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,季节流转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把我抛在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前分配文化祭任务的时候你不是请假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就决定你负责舞台了 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:05.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台…要做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:06.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搬东西的活让轻音部的人做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要负责时间安排之类轻松的事就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:15.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:21.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:26.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:27.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没有职务空缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不热了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的婚礼决定在春假举行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:42.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还体贴地亲自过来告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:46.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回家路上 我们稍微聊了会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦那家伙 还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然吓了你一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不啊 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你很明显地喜欢皆川老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你现在不戴眼镜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 眼镜坏了 顺便就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是她就叫你戴隐形眼镜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太明显了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是比较喜欢你戴眼镜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:36.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的哥哥会让我想起过去的他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口…稍微有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼你能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是肯定的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:19.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:35.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最终版正式表演的时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们这两天一直准备肯定很累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在就位前可以自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}但也请掌握好时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超有领导范啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对这个舞台工作她可是相当卖力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那里的男生A、B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要是敢迟到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我把你们丢进后夜祭的火堆里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总算做得差不多了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要和男朋友逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 没时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 感觉有些累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们去哪休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}想去个安静点的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那先吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要和谁待在一起什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然脑海里浮现出几个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是打消了这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里逛起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:33.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,距离就位还有些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里正在举行时装秀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请过来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多很棒的作品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}慢死了 你去干嘛了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 不然就要结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我对麦的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.37,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比你更长久 更真实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我现在痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也试着自己迈出脚步就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你很棒哦 欧端同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刺绣太精细了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你自己做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你平时穿的衣服也是手工做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以前就想问问看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 下次教我制作方法吧 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫最可…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也教教我吧 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫最可啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:19.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了 安乐冈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去帮大伙的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要搬哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赶得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快点动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:35.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 帮忙拿下线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:38.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉安乐冈同学 帮忙发下传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈 把那里的器材搬到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个！快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:05.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人自在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人能想清楚很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:20.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕孤身一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:34.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是孤单的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那这种事也没有意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:55.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在那天许下了约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀好僵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会相遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 愿意帮忙的人结业式以后都到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是庆祝老师的结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要做这么多的活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别讲话 麻溜点做事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是执行小组的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把那边不用的工具搬到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 又搬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都说快点搞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫森山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今年开始跟你同班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 安乐冈同学 快点把东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你和粟屋怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间都没看见你跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 请跟我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能别随意在这秀存在感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:20.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:39.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 刚才只是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你暂时还不想被他人告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\bord0\fn@方正卡通简体\fs90\c&H9237E4&\fad(200,0)\pos(710,549.8)}流-------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好温柔 小绘好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好我知道了 先擤下鼻涕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你再也不会和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:25.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你剪头发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是入学考试那时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天没有绑辫子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能摸摸看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,头发好顺滑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放下来果然是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那时不知为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种被接纳的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛就像第一次开始呼吸一般
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,世界接纳了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个发型也很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:35.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,清爽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1.05}祝钟井老师 皆川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1.05\an7}结婚快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不啊 真羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们一起写的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:11.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:16.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学是去老师们的婚礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 我还没去过结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:34.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和最喜欢的人白到头老
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:38.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔  花 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial\pos(919.2,993)}bouquet toss
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,扔什么 不是没扔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 可不能被抢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用 用不着你说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的约定也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,堆叠的日子也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经失去了意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初也只是寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以相濡以沫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一心思念着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:11.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的热心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:15.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经交换的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在情场失意的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 约定已经失效了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新的契约要重新缔结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H3A3A38&\fad(300,0)\frz347.7\blur1.5\pos(1336.8,640.601)}抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:40.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:45.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别道歉 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:02.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事先说明 茜姐变了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:03.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还是选择了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是很喜欢哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:23.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭宋_GBK\frz270\bord0\fad(500,1000)\c&H000000&\b1\pos(1033.8,567)}已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说出口也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麦也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到我们第一次回避了身体接触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:52.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了用语言来安慰对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是至今都没做过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说了各种各样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:01.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,连直到现在的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉 真漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:15.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说初恋是无法实现的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:22.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是秋天 却突然觉得很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,照亮着尘埃 空气缓缓流动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有着用旧的木头的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,时间永恒地一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我静静地呼吸着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:00.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到麦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在寻求着真正的那一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚知道这是无法轻易入手的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么许愿怎么祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能触碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:29.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下次会受更重的伤也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:35.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会更加地孤独也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:40.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,继续追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:50.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想分开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:51.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想别放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想留下你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想完结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:01.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:11.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使现在得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在寻找着真正的那一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:19.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:49.36,Kuzu_title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs82.5\frz270\bord0\c&H28262B&\b1\pos(708,774)\blur15\alpha&HF0\t(0,3400,1.5,\blur0\alpha&H00&)}两人的故事
